the democraticcontrolled congress is on 
summer vacation having calmed its internal strife but still 
searching for a political agenda to steal thunder from a popular 
president 
with the scandal and resignation of house speaker jim wright two 
months behind them democrats feel very positive i think were 
back on top we feel were in control said rep mike synar 
dokla 
democrats cite a rush of spending bills and other routine 
